w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe314252b-c6f7-4cd2-b20d-886ec95dfed5_904x777.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe314252b-c6f7-4cd2-b20d-886ec95dfed5_904x777.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe314252b-c6f7-4cd2-b20d-886ec95dfed5_904x777.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe314252b-c6f7-4cd2-b20d-886ec95dfed5_904x777.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这一切都是非常不人道的。然而，让这些 DSA 集会蒙羞的不仅仅是嗜血和偶尔的反犹太主义。集会的广告也<a href="https://twitter.com/RitchieTorres/status/1711055332548415627">提到了</a>“占领75年”。加沙和约旦河西岸于1967年被占领，距今已有56年历史。 75年前是以色列建国的日子，这意味着这些左翼分子<a href="https://twincitiesdsa.org/2023/10/twin-cities-dsa-statement-of-solidarity-with-palestine/">明确支持</a>哈马斯对以色列进行种族清洗的目标。</p><p>现在，有必要指出的是，据我所知，<em>所有</em>这些嗜血和对种族清洗的支持，100%，都<a href="https://twitter.com/ArmandDoma/status/1711191517942137017">来自草根阶层</a>，而不是来自社会主义政客或进步领导人。伯尼·桑德斯和<a href="https://ocasio-cortez.house.gov/media/press-releases/statement-rep-ocasio-cortez-violence-israel-and-palestine">AOC</a>都<a href="https://twitter.com/sensanders/status/1710654061618372659">强烈谴责</a>哈马斯的袭击。 “小队”呼吁以色列不要采取军事行动回应，这是极不现实的，但这并不构成对哈马斯的丝毫支持。多年来一直支持巴勒斯坦的伊丽莎白·沃伦（Elizabeth Warren）在听到有关哈马斯暴力行为的报道时<a href="https://twitter.com/JoshKraushaar/status/1711420664622592272">泪流满面</a>，她说：“我今天在这里明确表示，恐怖主义是没有任何理由的。”等等。多位纽约民主党<a href="https://twitter.com/bradlander/status/1711168969980166363">领导人</a><a href="https://www.nydailynews.com/2023/10/09/mayor-adams-says-dsa-backed-nyc-pols-must-soul-search-after-controversial-pro-palestine-rally-is-that-something-they-stand-for/">谴责</a>DSA 集会； AOC<a href="https://www.politico.com/news/2023/10/10/aoc-pro-palestine-nyc-rally-00120684">谴责</a>这次集会的“偏执和冷酷”。</p><p>即使在左翼草根阶层中，也没有一致赞扬哈马斯的战争罪行。一些有原则的社会主义者坚持正派： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image